Third-party and dataset documentation
=======================================

The directory `docs/knowledge-base/gee-datasets/markdown/` contains
markdown pages describing Google Earth Engine (GEE) datasets and related
geospatial products. These pages are derived from public Earth Engine dataset
catalog material and provider documentation (including citations and terms of
use as published by data owners).

If you redistribute this repository:

- Respect the **original license and terms** of each dataset and provider
  cited in the relevant markdown file.
- Treat this corpus as **reference documentation**, not a grant of rights to
  the underlying data or commercial use beyond what each provider allows.
- For authoritative, up-to-date descriptions, consult the official
  [Earth Engine Data Catalog](https://developers.google.com/earth-engine/datasets).

No warranty is made regarding completeness or legal suitability of the
mirrored text for any particular jurisdiction or use case.
